episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: When a professor gives Natalia some troubling news about the app she’s building for a tech competition, she's forced to pivot to a new idea.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Natalia decides to build an app that optimizes the female orgasm. But after realizing she’s clueless about it, she turns to Paulina and Monika for help.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: The girls visit a sex store to find the perfect research tool for their project. When they fail to do so, Natalia decides to make one herself.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: As Natalia and Paulina go to a sex trade show to learn more about intimacy, Monika embarks on her own quest to recruit subjects for their study.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Monika’s idea for gathering data is a hit, but Natalia isn’t happy with the results. The girls go to a class on female pleasure to gain more insight.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: After facing their parents at Easter breakfast, each of the girls needs to let off some steam. Luckily, there’s a wild party on the dorm’s rooftop.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: After getting an anonymous tip about the copulation lab, the dean investigates the girls’ project and threatens them with expulsion from the university.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: The big pitch at the university tech competition is upon the girls. They’ll have to decide: Are they willing to sacrifice everything to participate?

episodes.overview: Given Sexify's financial troubles, Monika must make a difficult decision to keep the business afloat. Natalia and Paulina search for test subjects.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Natalia and Adam spend the day together while Paulina explores the dating scene for research. Monika and Maks attend an unusual event.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: In light of the competition, Małgorzata pushes up the release date. After learning the truth about her father, Paulina reaches out to an old friend.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: While the coders stay behind to analyze data, Natalia, Monika and Paulina look to sex experts for help. Rafał's attempts to promote his app backfire.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: After receiving negative feedback, the Sexify founders seek to improve the user experience. Małgorzata and Monika have different visions for the company.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: While Sexify closes its doors, Natalia, Monika and Paulina take time apart to focus on themselves and recharge. Rafał receives an offer from Małgorzata.
